            <img src="/Assets/images/webd.jpg" alt="web-design-image" style="width:100%">
            <h3>Web Design</h3>
            <p>Creating and designing the visual layout, aesthetics, and user experience of your website. It involves a combination of graphic design, typography, color theory, and user interface (UI) principles to create visually appealing and functional websites. I focus on creating engaging and intuitive user interfaces that enhance the overall user experience.</p>
          </div>
